==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to [[make]] an [[example]] of'''
#{{idiom}} To [[punish]] someone so as to be a [[warning]] to others.
#* He '''made an example of''' the drunken sailor with twenty lashes, to show that he must have a sober crew

